### Comicif Backend API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/api/health/

###

### 2. API Root
GET http://localhost:8000/

###

### 3. Get Available Options (Backgrounds and Poses)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/available-options/

###

### 4. Process Photo (File Upload) - Always uses rembg
POST http://localhost:8000/api/process-photo/
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="test1.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test1.png
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="background"

space
--boundary--

###

### 5. Process Photo Base64 (JSON) - Always uses rembg
POST http://localhost:8000/api/process-photo-base64/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "photo_base64": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==",
    "background": "beach"
}

###

