### Variables for different environments
### Development
# @baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Production  
# @baseUrl = https://your-production-url.com

### Available backgrounds:
# - spiderman_building: Prédio da cidade (estilo Homem-Aranha)
# - goku_clouds: Nuvens no céu (estilo Dragon Ball)  
# - space: Espaço sideral
# - beach: Praia tropical
# - forest: Floresta mística

### Background removal:
# - Always uses rembg (AI-powered background removal)
# - No need to specify method parameter - it's automatic
# - High quality results with transparent backgrounds